The App makes use of functionality on your device that can pinpoint your location. We do this in order to show your position on your chosen walk. When you open the App for the first time, you will be asked whether the App can use your location and in what circumstances. You can change your choices at any time in the App settings and you can also turn the location services off at any time. The App’s functionality will be reduced if location services are turned off.
